結果】今日嘅攪珠結果係... (公測中)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1391078\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1391078</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<ins>3) 一班IT義士研發系統 v2.0 (網頁版+App版)</ins><br />\n【攪珠遊擊戰】攪珠系統 beta v2.0 (公測)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1393769\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1393769</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<ins>4) 第二次攪珠</ins><br />\n【8.1攪珠結果】今日嘅攪珠結果係...<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1394124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1394124</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">③ 暫時成效</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n［突然］深水埗開始多人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1391424\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1391424</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/02/091355_0a2342b0feb408807891b41fc1b09452.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F02%2F091355_0a2342b0feb408807891b41fc1b09452.png&h=1b7a1167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MSFb6FY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMSFb6FY.jpg&h=4257353b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(圖片轉載自於葵涌巴絲)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>④ 問題 </strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我認同有巴打認為咁嘅遊擊行動出師無名<br />\n但出師有名 = 經過宣傳 &ne; 遊擊<br />\n出師有名就冇辦法做到攻其不備<br />\n呢點方面歡迎討論<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果真係要講遊擊目的<br />\n① 令狗仔防守成本大增<br />\n② 早日令狗仔軍團崩潰<br />\n③ 達到be water嘅極致<br />\n④ 減少義士受傷被捕<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>⑤ 小結</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">無論如何<br />\n請各位密切留意<br />\n逢星期五新增嘅<br />\n「狗多寶獎金」<br />\n頭炮率先喺<br />\n今日 8.2 下午6時正<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> !!!開彩!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">立刻試玩，網頁版 攪珠系統 beta v2.0 (公測)&darr;&darr;&darr;</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hkhelper0001.github.io/restaurant/restaurant_spinner.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkhelper0001.github.io%2Frestaurant%2Frestaurant_spinner.html&d=7O3ztiABqAoAY%2BrF22wgzcF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=172c0237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkhelper0001.github.io/restaurant/restaurant_spinner.html</a> </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">想玩 App版 (限Android) 攪珠系統 beta v2.0 (公測) 入 今日嘅攪珠結果係...TG (Channel) &darr;&darr;&darr;</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/gaochu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fgaochu&d=7O3ztiABqAoAY%2BrF22wgzcF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=b53d7551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/gaochu</a></span><br />\n<br />\n[/b][/size=6][/red]<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins></ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"e9caa5c077911059beffb756ebf17679fd8b2f15","tid":1397072,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:17:12.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" c